{"tid":670761,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲做過後十字韌帶手術？","createTime":"2018-05-19T15:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T07:04:06.000Z","uid":186412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"37bc1d0dccc1d944508eba79d0d3b35ce304f94c","tid":670761,"uid":186412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"係咁嘅 小弟20歲<br />\n<br />\n我之前踢波俾人kick低膝頭地 <br />\n<br />\n一開始唔識嘢冇睇醫生 直接睇physio<br />\n<br />\n拖左2個月先去照MRI  知道斷晒後十字韌帶 前十字韌帶斷左一半<br />\n<br />\n醫生話要做後十字韌帶重建手術（PCL），前十字就冇得攪因為斷唔晒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我4月14號喺st paul做左個微創pcl，幾日後出院，依家戴左個穩定支架5個星期，維持0度，唔俾曲，靠枴杖行路。<br />\n<br />\n但醫生話一兩個星期後就拆得個架 行得翻路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但之後要勤力做物理治療。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問下各位巴打絲打 <br />\n你地康復進度係點㗎？手術完幾耐正常行得返？幾耐慢跑得？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，膝頭到依家都仲幾腫，係唔係有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n講埋你地幾歲，係咪做微創<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6646564cbe190a45f3652fcb8552b2bc3fddf88b","tid":670761,"uid":186412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/19/234247_809957c2104a1aae8946dd7938c4aded.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F19%2F234247_809957c2104a1aae8946dd7938c4aded.png&h=1dc80a33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隻腳依家咁 膝頭仲腫腫地 係咪正常？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大脾冇晒肌肉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76080f7eff943e2048f3b944ae02c9e77ba3b4b","tid":670761,"uid":186412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b5dd059c2595995578eb2a84633d0ed9008de2","tid":670761,"uid":186412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb96ab0c6382126f2dfe504fb13163784797ef30","tid":670761,"uid":186412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebb5f528f7ff7472cffba4ffdb4c58c021a9002","tid":670761,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:56:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d69e7339c86bd30d70efd546b473bfb18140798","tid":670761,"uid":186412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba8682da4d5eee857f842d74a67fd8dc6e25e5e","tid":670761,"uid":186412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=